Equity First Bank (San Francisco)
Nico Nebel
27.06.2026


// XA
NOTE MOVE TO START
LINK 800
LINK 800
LINK 800

NOTE COPY MAX 7 EXAS
COPY 800 X
MARK REPL_EXA
  REPL EXA_ACTION
  ADDI X 1 X
  TEST X < 806
  TJMP REPL_EXA

NOTE ACTION PER EXA
MARK EXA_ACTION
  LINK X
  COPY #CASH T
  
  MARK DISPENSE_BILLS
    TJMP BILL_AVAILABLE
    HALT
    MARK BILL_AVAILABLE
    COPY 20 #DISP
    SUBI T 1 T
    JUMP DISPENSE_BILLS